    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and will require significant mechanical work and cosmetic repairs to be roadworthy. The engine struggles to start and runs roughly, while the transmission exhibits noticeable slipping. The exterior has extensive rust, several large dents, and peeling paint, and the interior shows heavy wear with torn upholstery and non-functional electronics. It is being sold as-is, ideally for parts or as a major project for someone with mechanical expertise.",
